unhappy or cause you any trouble, so...

43:49.400 --> 43:51.200
...I'll go.

43:51.200 --> 43:55.800
I wish you every happiness.

44:18.600 --> 44:20.400
You have lovely friends.

44:20.500 --> 44:23.700
