- Great. Wonderful. Thank you.

44:46.000 --> 44:47.400
- Oh!
- What are you thinking?

44:47.500 --> 44:50.100
- You can't just give people money.
- You gave me money.

44:50.200 --> 44:53.500
- That's not the point.
- And she was very helpful.

44:53.500 --> 44:55.600
So, what's the deal,
this prince of yours?

44:55.600 --> 44:59.600
- How long you two been together?
- Oh, about a day.

44:59.600 --> 45:02.200
You mean it feels like a day
because you're so in love?

45:02.300 --> 45:06.100
- No. It's been a day.
- You're kidding me. A day?

45:06.200 --> 45:07.800
- One day?
- Yes.

45:07.900 --> 45:11.300
- And tomorrow will be two days.
- You're joking.

45:11.400 --> 45:13.200
- No. I'm not.
- Yeah, you are.

45:13.200 --> 45:14.800
But I'm not.

45:14.900 --> 45:18.500
You're gonna marry somebody after a day
because you fell in love with him?

45:18.500 --> 45:21.100
Yes.

45:21.100 --> 45:22.700
Yes!

45:27.400 --> 45:30.300
Oh! Ooh!

45:31.700 --> 45:34.300
I don't get it. How can you talk
about loving some guy

45:34.300 --> 45:37.500
- you don't even know?
- Well, I know what's in his heart.

45:37.600 --> 45:40.000
Oh, OK. Great.

45:40.100 --> 45:42.200
This was so yummy.

45:42.300 --> 45:44.500
I didn't know that food
could taste like this.

45:44.600 --> 45:46.900
