where I am right now.

52:19.602 --> 52:23.299
Sire! Oh dear, oh dear.

52:23.372 --> 52:27.138
- You've fallen on your royal...
- I know.

52:28.277 --> 52:29.574
Ah!

52:41.557 --> 52:43.388
- I love them so much.
- Really?

52:43.459 --> 52:46.485
Usually you send those e-mail cards
with the digital flowers.

52:46.562 --> 52:49.827
These are exquisite. Where do you find
live doves in New York City?

52:49.899 --> 52:52.766
- Oh, it's a long story.
- And these? Oh!

52:52.835 --> 52:54.962
- We're going to a ball?
- You don't have to.

52:55.037 --> 52:57.198
Are you kidding me?
It's so romantic.

52:57.273 --> 52:59.434
- So spontaneous!
- Good.

52:59.508 --> 53:02.671
- I can't wait.
- Good. Great.

53:02.745 --> 53:04.269
And...

53:04.347 --> 53:07.612
...as far as Giselle's concerned,
I'm just trying to help her.

53:07.683 --> 53:09.207
- Nothing's...
- You know what?

53:09.285 --> 53:13.949
If you say nothing happened,
nothing happened. I trust you.

53:14.023 --> 53:18.756
- So tomorrow night, then.
- This is so unlike you.

