54:04.740 --> 54:08.301
<i>They were dressed
all freaky. Then this chipmunk...</i>

54:08.377 --> 54:11.107
<i>I've always been in love with you.</i>

54:12.581 --> 54:16.017
<i>Don't you have any self-respect?</i>

54:18.054 --> 54:20.113
<i>I don't need self-respect.</i>

54:21.390 --> 54:23.153
<i>I just need your lips against mine.</i>

54:24.894 --> 54:28.853
Wait, sire!
Go back! Go back! Please!

54:28.931 --> 54:32.731
<i>How could I love a man
who doesn't even like himself?</i>

54:38.874 --> 54:42.332
<i>Get away from me, Jerry!
