Sad little chipmunk.

55:17.780 --> 55:21.181
Aw, deranged from exhaustion.

55:21.250 --> 55:25.380
Aw. Maybe you'd like to snuggle
in a nice little nook

55:25.454 --> 55:27.217
for the night, eh?

55:42.204 --> 55:44.399
Night-night.

55:46.876 --> 55:49.674
Sleep tight.

55:49.745 --> 55:52.339
I think I need some air, sire.

55:55.718 --> 55:58.846
<i>I don't like them sad endings.</i>

56:02.258 --> 56:03.850
Sire.

56:04.593 --> 56:06.993
Do you...

56:07.062 --> 56:08.427
...like yourself?

56:10.032 --> 56:12.023
What's not to like?

57:03.886 --> 57:05.353
Where'd he go?

57:07.089 --> 57:09.717
<i># When the moon hits your eye</i>

57:09.792 --> 57:12.522
<i># Like a big pizza pie...</i>

57:12.595 --> 57:15.086
Oh, yeah. Here.
Watch this.

57:15.164 --> 57:18.930
Watch very carefully. I'm gonna
put it in this hand like that.

57:19.001 --> 57:21.731
Oh, do it again! Show me!
That's wonderful.

57:21.804 --> 57:23.897
